      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Five-point hemolysis validation against FDA experimental benchmark",
      "description": "CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index compared against FDA PIV and hemolysis experimental data at 5 flow-speed operating points. Mean normalized RMS error 7.3%. All predictions within 15% of experimental mean. UQ sensitivity sweeps (12 parameters, LHS n=128) embedded; scalar sensitivity indices reported in supporting technical report TR-2024-07. The structured hasSensitivityAnalysis link is omitted here per MRL 2 reporting convention; sensitivity findings are fully described in TR-2024-07 and referenced from this validation result narrative.",
      "passFail": "Pass",
      "quantitativeMetric": "Mean NRMSE = 7.3%; max individual point error = 14.1%"
    },
    {
